formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
The architect certificate is formatted in a such a way that entire work is bifurcated into various activities and architech is required to cerfity percentage of work completion of such activities  The architect certificate does not provide overall percentage of work completed of the project  This being a technical matter we are not in a position to comment upon whether physical work completed as per architect certificate is in coherence with acutal expenditure incurred and paid		
		
		
		
		
		
Difference up to 10 percentage  between expenditure
incurred as per Engineer certificate vis a vis expenditure incurred as per books of account is considered as physical work completed is in coherence with actual expenditure incurred and paid
During the quarter amount received from rera account is inclusive of GST. Where as for the purpose of received amount net off gst amount considered.		
In case of carpet area of booked inventories and unit consideration for booked and unbooked inventories, date of sale agreement, KYC are as certified by the promotor. 		
During the period firm received Bu Permisision for the project. Therefore in that case they executed sale deed without entering into Agreement to sale in the case where full amount received
